external_knowledge:
- "Seen action in the market" implies having at least one sale; 
- "Been viewed" and "been reviewed" imply having at least one view and review respectively; 
- "Located somewhere" implies having a recorded location;
- "Spaciousness" refers to the above-ground living area (`gr_liv_area`).

sql:
SELECT total_bsmt_sf, overall_quality
FROM properties
WHERE property_id = (SELECT MAX(property_id) FROM properties);
